                <iframe class="youtubeplayer" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kiDx_Hi59Eo?rel=0&amp;enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" enablejsapi="1" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            <div class="youtubeplayerOverlay" style="background-image:url('https://img.youtube.com/vi/kiDx_Hi59Eo/0.jpg');">
                    <span class="youtube-modal-link">
                        <span>
                            <i class="fa fa-youtube-play"></i>
                                <h3>360 degrees in Za&#39;atari refugee camp</h3>
                                                            <span>Mahmoud, 15, arrived at the Jordanian refugee camp Za&#39;atari in 2012 along with his parents and six siblings. He gives us a 360 degree view of how his life has changed since then. </span>
                                                    </span>
                    </span>
            </div>
